{"type": "article", "id": 24244, "title": "像手提袋一样的垃圾袋", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-22T07:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702164245oXaC8cbG09qmusNz.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个垃圾筒使用了可回收塑料，像是直接由普通牛皮纸袋子做成的，只有黑白两色，方正而简单。但它的优点也在于这种清爽简洁，给环境的影响很弱，可以融入现代的家庭厨房到办公环境中。设计者的初衷也有环保的想法，让超市或商店都使用纸口袋，提回来之后，可以放在里面用做垃圾袋了。产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/20614143/rebin-the-modern-alternative-to-traditional-recycl?ref=nav_search\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021642432k6A8YTMnweOqo7H.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164244fJZtFMRkjP8N0zuO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164244PFoY5HDf3hpK0y2Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164245Xa1kHB08SdDu9zrZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}